{"tid":1774233,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《龍與虎》動畫的隱晦暗示，逢阪大河電車內八扭腿","createTime":"2019-12-08T06:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:21:12.000Z","uid":109809,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6f328819b604e2e4f34a5a33470a5bd1e05586","tid":1774233,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"25集中，故事進入了收尾階段，龍兒和大河也終於走到了一起，還上演了一幕兩人深夜KISS的場面，可謂十分溫馨。<br />\n<br />\n兩人坐上了電車，這時候兩個人的手已經緊緊握在了一起，有一種新婚小夫妻的感覺，而事實上確實是如此。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfzyDXX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfzyDXX.gif&h=a2d83cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就在25集8分25秒左右，逢坂大河突然毫無徵兆地內八扭了兩下腿，就好像哪裡不舒服一樣，在最初看這裡的時候，估計沒有一個人會去注意這個小細節。<br />\n<br />\n實際上這個細節是主創團隊特意加的，人設田中將賀在訪談裡有提到了這個，這個細節就是暗示龍兒和大河前一天晚上已經畢業了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJUyDXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJUyDXW.jpg&h=e6b169ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33347fd99c09f6cbdbda1bbb1e611f0cdc9facae","tid":1774233,"uid":247139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"o"},{"pid":"db9186c8e724e3395d08226cf8e6ba4801f200ba","tid":1774233,"uid":175590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">3點鐘 維園見 早D出門口呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488205f9b1aae445a196636e2d6b5ce7c348fa79","tid":1774233,"uid":249979,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda4